wiki.summary: Schizophrenia is a mental disorder that affects a person’s perception of reality, often including auditory and visual hallucinations. In many cases, the person affected by the disease will withdraw from personal relationships and reality in general. X raps in his song, “ghost”: "Bleed red, four doors in the Benz But I met four ghosts in the pen." While this could just be a metaphor, visual hallucinations are a major symptom of schizophrenia. Read more on Last.fm.
